-| Date | Note |
-|---|---|
-| 2026-05-18 | Plan written — 4 steps, 4 files (1 new). No safety gates triggered. Pre-existing failures in task-card.test.tsx: 4 dueDate tests (schema has no dueDate field — out of scope for this task). |
